                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The forge-spurned breathes a cloud of stinging soot, ash, and glowing embers. This can affect either a @Template[type:cone|distance:30] or a @Template[type:burst|distance:20] centered on the forge-spurned and persists for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<p>Each creature that moves into or starts their turn in the area takes @Damage[6d6[fire]] damage, with a @Check[type:reflex|dc:21|basic:true] save. A creature that fails its save is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>Creatures within the cloud are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed], though not from the forge-spurned.</p>\n<p>The forge-spurned can't use Forge Breath again until it has used Inflate Bellows.</p>"
                },
